sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant Admin as Admin / User
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant WVA as WVA Controller<br/>(controller-manager)
    participant Prom as Prometheus / Thanos<br/>9091/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant vLLM as vLLM Servers<br/>8200/TCP HTTP
    participant EPP as EPP (Gateway API Ext)<br/>Scheduler Metrics
    participant HPA as HPA / KEDA
    participant Deploy as Deployment / LWS

    rect rgb(220, 240, 255)
        Note over WVA,Prom: Flow 1: Saturation-Based Autoscaling Decision
        WVA->>Prom: PromQL: KV cache utilization, queue depth<br/>HTTPS/9091 | Bearer Token (SA)
        Prom-->>WVA: Metric values per pod/model<br/>HTTPS/9091 | TLS 1.2+
        Note over WVA: Saturation V2 Engine computes<br/>token-based capacity model
        Note over WVA: Pipeline: Optimizer → Enforcer → GPU Limiter
        Note over WVA: Cache decision: wva_desired_replicas={N}
        Prom->>WVA: Scrape /metrics endpoint<br/>HTTPS/8443 | Bearer Token
        WVA-->>Prom: wva_desired_replicas metric
        HPA->>Prom: Read external metric<br/>HTTPS/9091 | Bearer Token
        Prom-->>HPA: wva_desired_replicas={N}
        HPA->>K8sAPI: PATCH scale subresource<br/>HTTPS/6443 | SA Token
        K8sAPI->>Deploy: Update replicas={N}
    end

    rect rgb(220, 255, 220)
        Note over WVA,EPP: Flow 2: Scale-from-Zero Detection
        WVA->>Prom: PromQL: EPP flow control queue size<br/>HTTPS/9091 | Bearer Token (SA)
        Prom-->>WVA: Queue size > 0 for idle model
        Note over WVA: Scale-from-Zero Engine detects<br/>pending requests on zero-replica model
        Note over WVA: Emit wva_desired_replicas=1
        Prom->>WVA: Scrape /metrics<br/>HTTPS/8443
        WVA-->>Prom: wva_desired_replicas=1
        HPA->>Prom: Read metric
        Prom-->>HPA: wva_desired_replicas=1
        HPA->>K8sAPI: Scale Deployment to 1<br/>HTTPS/6443
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 220)
        Note over Admin,WVA: Flow 3: ConfigMap Dynamic Configuration Update
        Admin->>K8sAPI: Update ConfigMap<br/>(thresholds, scale-to-zero policy)
        K8sAPI-->>WVA: Watch event (ConfigMap change)
        Note over WVA: ConfigMap Reconciler validates<br/>and updates in-memory config
        Note over WVA: Next engine cycle reads new config<br/>(no restart required)
    end

    rect rgb(245, 220, 255)
        Note over WVA,Prom: Flow 4: Queueing Model SLO-Driven Scaling
        WVA->>Prom: PromQL: TTFT, ITL histograms<br/>HTTPS/9091 | Bearer Token (SA)
        Prom-->>WVA: Latency percentile data
        Note over WVA: Queueing Model Engine:<br/>M/M/1/K model + Kalman filter<br/>parameter learning
        Note over WVA: Compare predicted latency vs SLO targets
        Note over WVA: Compute required replicas for SLO compliance
    end

    rect rgb(255, 230, 230)
        Note over WVA,vLLM: Metrics Collection (Continuous)
        vLLM-->>Prom: Push/scrape vLLM metrics<br/>HTTP/8200
        EPP-->>Prom: Push/scrape EPP metrics
        Note over Prom: Aggregates: KV cache, queue depth,<br/>tokens, latency, throughput,<br/>scheduler dispatch rate
    end
